Task 0

A server is a machine/software that provides resources to one or more client machines in a request-response manner.

The domain name makes it easier to locate the server on the web.

www is an A record that matches a domain name to an IP address.

Web server provides access to server from the web. Application server runs the application e.g. if it's a framework like Django. Database stores and performs poerations on data.

Server uses http or https to communicate with computers requesting website.

ISSUES
SPOF because there is only one server.
Maintenance can also lead to downtime due to lack of backup server.
